        "_Dil Bechara_ (qv) traces the emotional journey of two hopelessly in love youngsters a young girl (Kizie) suffering from cancer, and a boy (Manny) who she meets at a support group. The two explore the funny, thrilling, and tragic adventure of being alive and in love.::sankeerth-06048",
        "A young Kizzie Basu is suffering from Thyroid Cancer and is dependent on an oxygen cylinder all her life she feels her life is very much boring and has a dream to meet singer Abhimanyu Veer who has left one of his songs incomplete since many years.During cancer counseling sessions she meets Immanuel Rajkumar Junior a fan of Superstar Rajnikanth and also suffering from Osteosarcoma.Immanuel and his friend JP whose suffering from glaucoma are making a film similar to Rajnikant's film and offer Kizzie a lead role.During this phase Kizzie's life changes and its no more boring Immanuel and she falls in love but death can call them anytime.::alex.mjacko@gmail.com"
